\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
HexInputServer allows users to input arbitrary Unicode characters by typing their corresponding hexadecimal values.  You could write a more complete and complex input server by modifying this example.  This sample demonstrates the basic usage of the AppKit Text Input API features including:\
\
- core text input interaction of insertText: & setMarkedText: methods\
- multiple input client context management\
- various client state (i.e. active/inactive) notification handling\
- status item/menu management\
- auxiliary window management\
- keyboard command handling via doCommandBySelector: method\
